2.2 Dusky rockfish

Generally speaking exploring different VAST models. The model variants are listed in the legends where db = design-based and the VAST models are listed by their error structure and the number of knots i.e., gamma_750 = a Gamma error structure with 750 knots.

2.3 Northern rockfish

Examinations of different weightings for the survey index of abundance. Survey weight is in percent. The srv_wt_100_var is a full weight VAST survey with the variance doubled.
